{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2ac2f6a6d6","title":"中央组织部、统战部关于党内外干部审查、分配问题的规定","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"49f6bd1bdd","index":0,"year":1950,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"2ac2f6a6d6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d113009fe4","type":"title","text":"中央组织部、统战部关于党内外干部审查、分配问题的规定","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2ac2f6a6d6"},{"id":"d03a678a27","type":"paragraph","text":"一、党的干部由党委组织部负责。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2ac2f6a6d6"},{"id":"d5066b8b21","type":"paragraph","text":"二、一般党外干部由政府人事部门负责。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2ac2f6a6d6"},{"id":"c49be242dc","type":"paragraph","text":"三、各民主党派干部、民主人士及旧社会上层人物（如开明士绅、学者等）的审查分配，则由各级统战部（无统战部门之地区由党委指定专人）提出意见与政府党组商量后交人事部门处理，或对政府党组征求统战部意见后交人事部门处理。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2ac2f6a6d6"},{"id":"51935c38e0","type":"paragraph","text":"对上述人员的任用向上级请示与向下级答覆，均用党委名义。党内得到批准后，再由政府以正式手续任命。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2ac2f6a6d6"}],"page":{"id":"bd874efb9a","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2ac2f6a6d6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}